import React from "react";
import {
  Box, Card, Typography, Avatar, Button, Divider
} from "@mui/material";
import ShoppingCartIcon from "@mui/icons-material/ShoppingCart";
import WalletIcon from "@mui/icons-material/AccountBalanceWallet";
import StarIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Star";

const cardStyle = {
  minHeight: 110,
  display: "flex",
  flexDirection: "row",
  alignItems: "center",
  borderRadius: 3,
  boxShadow: 5,
  p: 3,
  pr: 5,
  mr: 3,
  my: 1.5,
  bgcolor: "#fff"
};

const detailCardStyle = {
  minHeight: 180,
  minWidth: 370,
  flex: 1,
  borderRadius: 3,
  boxShadow: 4,
  p: 3.5,
  m: 0,
  bgcolor: "#fff"
};

const UserDashboard = () => (
  <Box sx={{
    bgcolor: "#fff5f7",
    minHeight: "100vh",
    width: "100vw",
    overflow: "auto"
  }}>
    {/* Header */}
    <Box
      sx={{
        bgcolor: "#e23744",
        color: "#fff",
        py: 4,
        px: 7,
        borderBottomLeftRadius: 32,
        borderBottomRightRadius: 32,
        minHeight: 130,
        boxShadow: 2,
        display: "flex",
        alignItems: "center",
        justifyContent: "space-between",
      }}
    >
      <Box display="flex" alignItems="center">
        <Avatar
          sx={{
            width: 76, height: 76,
            bgcolor: "#fff", color: "#e23744",
            fontWeight: 700, fontSize: 36, mr: 3
          }}
        >U</Avatar>
        <Box>
          <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight={900} sx={{ letterSpacing: 1 }}>
            Welcome, [User Name]!
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" fontWeight={500} sx={{ opacity: .95 }}>
            Doorstep fuel delivery, made easy.
          </Typography>
        </Box>
      </Box>
      <Button
        variant="contained"
        sx={{
          bgcolor: "#fff",
          color: "#e23744",
          borderRadius: 99,
          px: 6, py: 1.2,
          fontWeight: 700,
          fontSize: 18,
          '&:hover': { bgcolor: "#ffb0b9" }
        }}
      >
        MY ACCOUNT
      </Button>
    </Box>
    {/* Metrics Row */}
    <Box
      sx={{
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "row",
        justifyContent: "flex-start",
        width: "100%",
        px: 7,
        pt: 7,
        pb: 3,
        flexWrap: "nowrap",
        overflowX: "auto"
      }}
    >
      {/* Loyalty */}
      <Card sx={cardStyle}>
        <StarIcon sx={{ color: "#e23744", fontSize: 44, mr: 2 }} />
        <Box>
          <Typography fontWeight={700} sx={{ color: "#e23744", opacity: 0.8 }}>
            Available Loyalty
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight={900}>₹0</Typography>
        </Box>
      </Card>
      {/* Wallet */}
      <Card sx={cardStyle}>
        <WalletIcon sx={{ color: "#e23744", fontSize: 44, mr: 2 }} />
        <Box>
          <Typography fontWeight={700} sx={{ color: "#e23744", opacity: 0.8 }}>
            My Wallet Limit
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight={900}>₹0</Typography>
        </Box>
      </Card>
      {/* Cart */}
      <Card sx={cardStyle}>
        <ShoppingCartIcon sx={{ color: "#e23744", fontSize: 44, mr: 2 }} />
        <Box>
          <Typography fontWeight={700} sx={{ color: "#e23744", opacity: 0.8 }}>
            Cart Status
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h5" fontWeight={900}>Active</Typography>
        </Box>
      </Card>
    </Box>
    <Divider sx={{ my: 2, mx: 7 }} />
    {/* Details Row */}
    <Box
      sx={{
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "row",
        justifyContent: "flex-start",
        width: "100%",
        px: 7,
        pb: 6,
        gap: 3
      }}
    >
      {/* Last 5 Orders */}
      <Card sx={detailCardStyle}>
        <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={900} sx={{ letterSpacing: 1, color: "#e23744" }}>
          My Last 5 Orders
        </Typography>
        <Divider sx={{ my: 1.5 }} />
        <Typography sx={{ opacity: 0.7 }}>No records found</Typography>
      </Card>
      {/* My Assets */}
      <Card sx={detailCardStyle}>
        <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={900} sx={{ letterSpacing: 1, color: "#e23744" }}>
          My Assets
        </Typography>
        <Divider sx={{ my: 1.5 }} />
        <Typography sx={{ opacity: 0.7 }}>No records found</Typography>
      </Card>
    </Box>
  </Box>
);

export default UserDashboard;
